    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, adheres to the most exacting standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled quality, meticulously maintained and completely free of discernable wear. We invite the most particular buyers to inspect this masterfully kept example.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
