      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe, a definitive specimen of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 era. This vehicle exhibits concours-level preservation with original paint depth and zero bolster wear on the Novillo leather interior. Mechanically, the engine utilizes a 12.0:1 compression ratio to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp, tactile engagement, transferring power through a GKN ViscoLok limited-slip differential. Proactive maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system operates within factory tolerances. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for variable compression and rebound adjustment. This is a turn-key, mechanically superlative example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Garage kept.",
      "price": 46500.0,
