    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed on a monthly basis. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the Black Dakota leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin retains its original new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect; a complete service history is documented through BMW, with all fluids and filters changed ahead of schedule. The tires are fresh, and the wheels are free of any curb rash. This is a turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior cabin that remains in showroom condition. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a benchmark of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
