    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, is absolutely spotless inside and out, and runs like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
